beer.beer_name: The Cool Kids – Tropical Citrus Berry Oat Cream IPA
beer.beer_description: The Cool Kids vol. 26 from Frenchies and Hopsters is tropical and fluffy with a smooth body thanks to the presence of lactose. This must-try Oat Cream IPA features hints of berries, plus a unique combination of passionfruit, coconut and guava flavours.
